OL,5, Matthew Fowler, who lost his father Ian
OL,6, to Covid in April 2020, has told the   
OL,7, Covid Inquiry that he has received     
OL,8, abuse online after speaking about the  
OL,9, virus.                                 
OL,11,FHe is co-founder of Covid-19 Bereaved  
OL,12,FFamilies for Justice, which campaigns  
OL,13,Fto learn lessons from the pandemic.    
OL,15,FMr Fowler spoke of how people from his 
OL,16,Forganisation have been "stalked via    
OL,17,Fsocial media".                         
OL,19,FHe added that others had been          
OL,20,F"threatened".                          
